{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A NEW SPACE <i>ROGUELITE</i></strong></h2><br>Face enemy waves and survive this hostile universe!<br><br>Equip yourself and to explore everything within your reach before it's too late.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845520/extras/Enemies_GIF.gif?t=1733218574\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ARM YOURSELF, CREATE SYNERGIES, DESTROY YOUR ENEMIES</strong></h2><br>Weapons evolve at your will; discover which ones best suit your playstyle, combine them with mysterious Techs, and harness the most powerful synergies the universe has to offer. The only limit to combinations is your imagination.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845520/extras/Tech_GIF.gif?t=1733218574\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WHAT MYSTERIES LIE HIDDEN?</strong></h2><br>Each game is unique: the setting, waves, and progression are governed by random algorithms. Forge your own path in this open environment and uncover what's happening around you. The ruins of an ancient civilization watch over you: don't meet the same fate as the Ancients.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845520/extras/ancient_ruins.png?t=1733218574\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Civilization and resource management<br></li><li>Combat with bullet hell elements<br></li><li>Frenzied encounters<br></li><li>Seven different weapon types, each with its own evolution tree and characteristics<br></li><li>Over 30 Techs that change the gameplay from match to match<br></li><li>Endless combinations of weapons and Techs<br></li><li>Unique, entirely original environment and universe<br></li><li>A hidden story to discover<br></li><li>Hidden mechanics</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/28